# Zaion - Decentralized OS

# Introduction

# Idea

We want to build a system which focuses the visualization of complex datas
with quick and simple to use tools which can traverse and display
datas in form of complex graphs. The goal is to build a native os built on top of linux/unix
systems. The system will be based on the IPFS protocol, not on a "usual" filesystem,
delivering built-in tools for data encryption and distribution.

## Hardware server for local-first applications

##

# Roadmap

- build distributed system on raspberry
- design a case for the raspberries
- release apps
  - presale token
  - nft-pfp mint
  - digital-content gate
    - album
    - single
- release a white paper for peer to peer stock management
- release a white paper for peer to peer distribution

